name 'programming-fundamentals-preassessment-intro_pilot-2025'
title 'Programming Fundamentals Pre-Assessment'
markdown <<MARKDOWN
This assessment is designed to gauge your prior knowledge of computational thinking, algorithms, variables, loops, conditionals, debugging, and other programming fundamentals.

- You are **not expected to know all the answers**! This is just to see what you already understand.
- Read each question carefully and **choose the best answer** based on what you know.
- There are **no penalties for incorrect answers**, so do your best!
MARKDOWN
